sentences: Cade launched his solo endeavors with his EP, 'Care', which was released in July 2016 via Spinnin' Records.
"Care" was produced by Cheat Codes' Trevor Dahl, who befriended Larson on a tour in 2015.

In 2017, he collaborated with pop trio, Cheat Codes, to remix Maggie Lindemannâ€™s "Pretty Girl", which resulted in over 700 million streams on Spotify alone, achieving Platinum certification in the US, and platinum certification in the UK.
Later in the year, CADE and Cheat Codes paired up again to collaborate on "Stay with You", peaking at 35 on the US Hot Dance/Electronic Songs Chart.
On June 23, CADE inked his first exclusive record deal with ULTRA MUSIC/Sony.
